

## **ESP8266 — Kitchen Node Wiring**

| ESP8266 Pin | Connected To        | Notes                  |
| ----------- | ------------------- | ---------------------- |
| D2          | DHT11 DATA          | Temperature & Humidity |
| A0          | MQ2 ANALOG          | Gas Sensor Reading     |
| 3.3V        | VCC of both sensors | Power Supply           |
| GND         | GND of both sensors | Ground                 |

---

## **ESP32 — Main Hub Wiring**

| ESP32 Pin | Connected To        | Notes                  |
| --------- | ------------------- | ---------------------- |
| GPIO4     | DHT11 DATA          | Temperature & Humidity |
| GPIO34    | MQ2 ANALOG          | Gas Sensor Reading     |
| GPIO35    | Water Sensor ANALOG | Water Level Detection  |
| GPIO18    | Passive Buzzer +    | Alarm Output           |
| 3.3V      | VCC of all sensors  | Power Supply           |
| GND       | GND of all sensors  | Ground                 |

---

